    "summary": "I have studied intensively  cosmology, physics and science .......in order to develop .......an out of the box theory about the pre Big Bang situation. Quantum mechanics...... and the theory of relativity were devaloped  more than 100 years ago. They are still apart for more than100 years, because they are fundamentally incompatible. \n\nArticles about major physics problems appear........ in the Scientific American magazine. The chief editors even stated that there is........ a crisis in cosmology and physics.\n\nTime to look at it in....... a new out of the box way. A new frame of reference........ to place nature's constants, speed of light ......and the entanglement of time ......and space, super position ......and wave-particle duality in......... a new out of the box frame. \n\nI have written a book ; The world according to the Spirit ; delivering the answers and evidence of the questions and themes on www.searchingforanswersaboutbigbang.com.(1600 positive reactions all over the world )\n\nExperienced manager and director, good at problem analysis and good at organizational optimization and structure improvement and improvement processes. \n\nActive for a year as coordinator for the North Holland Energy Cooperative NHEC to manage energy coaches to reduce the energy consumption of households with specific advice. With data analysis and inspection of the building construction, we arrive at targeted and efficient advice to save energy and live more sustainably. \n\nIn addition to the work as an energy coach, as a North Holland Energy Cooperative  NHEC, we try to fill large roofs of industrial areas and social real estate with solar panels with the participation of local residents. For example ......, I am a participant in various regional working groups to stimulate a sustainable energy transition . \n\nSince 2018 active as councilor for the CDA in the municipality of Schagen and active as committee member. \n\nI have been an owner of a printery for more than 25 years.I have been a chairman for several inter local social and commercial  organisations to cooperate with several institutions.I have studied HBO commercial and business economics.I deliver my experience and knowledge to solve business and organisation problems.",
